abstract: Los Angeles County District Atty's Office declines to pursue sexual assault charges against Bill Cosby, saying criminal charges are blocked by statute of limitations or lack sufficient evidence.
lead_paragraph: Los Angeles County prosecutors cited the statute of limitations and insufficient evidence in saying no charges would be filed in two cases.

headline.main: Bill Cosby Inquiries in California to Be Dropped
headline.print_headline: Cosby Inquiries in California to Be Dropped
